            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Taycan]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1233377</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>保时捷第三代 Panamera 车系正式到香港，早前于全新开幕的香港保时捷旗舰陈列室举行了传媒发布会。小编都有代表 unwire 出席，以下就详细同大家睇睇！</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1233402 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_145826-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_145826-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_145826-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1233401 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_153317-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_153317-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_153317-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233380" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0023-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0023-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0023.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233381" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0022-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0022-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0022.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Panamera 运动型豪华房车的领军车款，已隆重进驻湾仔全新旗舰陈列室。保时捷 Panamera 升级至第三代车款，进一步提升 E-Hybrid 混合动力技术和高阶主动式底盘控制系统。加入大量创新技术包括 Porsche Active Ride 悬挂系统，能够结合运动驾驶模式与令人满意的舒适度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233382" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0000-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0000-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0000.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233383" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0001-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0001-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0001.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>第三代保时捷 Panamera 拥有优雅的车身设计，外观科技感十足。长度为 5,052 mm（行政加长版为 5,202 mm），宽度 1,937 mm，高度 1,423 mm（行政加长版为 1,428 mm）。重新设计的进气口满足了动力传动系统的需求，车身线条和比例依旧保留车系的特色，侧窗线条进一步强化四门跑车的特征。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233385" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0008-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0008-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0008.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>车厢内，Porsche Driver Experience 结合数码化与实体触控方式，所有操作介面及显示概念以驾驶者为中心设计。Normal、Sport 和 Sport Plus 模式开关也在驾驶者可轻松触及的范围内，方便驾驶时快速切换。副驾乘客亦可利用 10.9 吋显示屏幕查看性能数据或观看影片与享受娱乐系统。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233388" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0014-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0014-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0014.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233389" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0016-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0016-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0016-rotated.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>中控台上 Panamera 结合保时捷通讯管理系统（PCM），驾驶者可将自己的线上帐户与车辆连接，并通过 Apple CarPlay 和 Android Auto 连接电话及车辆数据，提升便利性。MyPorsche 应用程序整合进 Apple CarPlay 中，进一步提升了可用性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233386" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0009-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0009-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0009.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233387" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0010-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0010-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0010.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在科技方面，Panamera 标配 LED 矩阵光束大灯，提供更好的照明。可选的 HD-LED 矩阵光束大灯，照明范围可达 600 公尺。辅助系统如 Porsche InnoDrive 与交通标志辨识系统协同工作，实现主动道路引导。新车型还提供了远端停车辅助功能，驾驶者可透过智能手机监控停车操作。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233391" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0018-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0018-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0018.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233390" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0005-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0005-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0005.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233404" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_154827-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_154827-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_154827-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>驾驶安全系统包括突破性的底盘科技 Porsche Active Ride 悬挂系统，标配主动式双阀门气压减震器，能独立调整压缩和回弹，减轻路面冲击的同时提高动态驾驶的稳定性。E-Hybrid 车型更能选配这一悬吊系统，提供前所未有的平衡。</p><p>全新 E-Performance 技术为 E-Hybrid 车型提供更强性能和续航。Panamera Turbo E-Hybrid 采用 4.0 公升双涡轮增压 V8 引擎搭配 140 kW 摩打，总输出达 500 kW（680PS）、最高扭力为 930Nm，0-100 km/h 加速仅需 3.2 秒，最高车速可达 315km/h。Panamera 车款则搭载 2.9 公升 V6 双涡轮增压引擎，输出功率达 260 kW (353PS)、峰值扭力 500Nm，并搭载重新设计的八速 PDK 变速箱，实现轻量化和更高持续输出。基本款 Panamera 从静止加速到 100 km/h 的时间缩短至 5.1 秒，并将最高车速提升至 272 km/h。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233392" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0019-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0019-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0019.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233394" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0002-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0002-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0002.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新 Panamera 车系已登陆座落于湾仔核心地段的全新香港保时捷旗舰陈列室。</p><p>全新 <b>Panamera </b>现已接受订购，售价为：</p><p>Panamera 港币 $1,838,000 起</p><p>Panamera Turbo E-Hybrid<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span>$3,768,000 起</p><p><i>*</i>制造商建议零售价 (包括首次登记税)<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><h2>Panamera 规格</h2><p>动力：2.9 公升 V6 双涡轮增压引擎</p><p>输出功率： 260 kW (353PS)</p><p>峰值扭力：500Nm</p><p>0-100km/h 加速时间：5.1 秒</p><p>最高车速：272 km/h</p><h2>Panamera Turbo E-Hybrid 规格</h2><p>动力：4.0 公升双涡轮增压 V8 引擎搭配 140 kW 摩打</p><p>输出功率：500 kW（680PS）</p><p>峰值扭力：930Nm</p><p>0-100 km/h 加速时间：3.2 秒</p><p>最高车速：315km/h</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/13/vehicles-getting-increasingly-problematic/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">J.D. Power 报告指电动车问题多　美国最可靠车款为 Porsche 718</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/08/taycan-2/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">保时捷纯电跑车 Taycan 小改款，性能更强 + 续航力提升三成</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/04/porsche-panamera-2024/life-tech/auto/">保时捷第三代 Panamera Turbo E-Hybrid 抵港，车身设计、车厢内部科技抢先睇</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
